狗来刨土","就是普通的装饰花纹","工匠随手刻着玩的","这是代表生命循环的意思"],["A","B","C"],["\"我记得自己曾经保护过一个幼小的生命...那个孩子那么小，那么安静。但让我不解的是，为什么我的底部要开一个小孔？每当月光透过那个小孔照进来，我总觉得能听到轻柔的摇篮曲...这是为什么？\""," \"有个画面一直萦绕在我心头：我被小心翼翼地安放在一座房屋旁边，而不是在远处的墓地。每天清晨，都能听到屋内传来的说话声和笑声...为什么要把我放在离生活这么近的地方？\"","\"我身上的纹路像编织的篮子，又像缠绕的丝线...每当月光照亮这些图案，我总觉得它们在轻轻蠕动。这些纹路到底想告诉人们什么秘密？\""],-2,[3,"aa9SBvo8JLJ5dmeq83vrgD"],0,1,2,3,4,5,6]],[4,"d4OQ06ZV5HNI2Xa4AYWTWL",null,null,null,-1,0]]],0,[0,1,1,0,2,1,0,3,1,2],[0,0,0,0,0,0,0],[4,5,6,7,8,9,10],[1,2,3,4,5,6,7]],[[{"name":"weng-hui","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":578,"height":568},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":578,"height":568},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-289,-284,0,289,-284,0,-289,284,0,289,284,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,568,578,568,0,0,578,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-289,"y":-284,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":289,"y":284,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[0],0,[0],[0],[8]],[[{"name":"weng-d","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":458,"height":585},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0.5},"originalSize":{"width":458,"height":586},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-229,-292.5,0,229,-292.5,0,-229,292.5,0,229,292.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,586,458,586,0,1,458,1],"nuv":[0,0.0017064846416382253,1,0.0017064846416382253,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-229,"y":-292.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":229,"y":292.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[0],0,[0],[0],[9]],[[{"name":"jieshao-wengguanzang","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":966,"height":407},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":966,"height":407},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-483,-203.5,0,483,-203.5,0,-483,203.5,0,483,203.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,407,966,407,0,0,966,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-483,"y":-203.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":483,"y":203.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}]